description:
The Second Adventist Camp Meeting in October 1868; and other happenings [History]

This week, we'll take a brief look at some notable events in the Seventh-day Adventist Church from October 2 to 8 in previous years.

Watch the video as Pastor David Trim recounts significant events that have helped strengthen and flourish the Seventh-day Adventist Church.

Discover more exciting happenings for the Seventh-day Adventist Church at https://encyclopedia.adventist.org/ 

Learn more about the Adventist Church and what we believe at https://www.adventist.org/
